ValidationDetailForm is a Form
    Layout
        display as text
            visible when (ValidationFailed)
                header3 of "<ConfigSnapshotItemInfo.Name>ValidationStatus"
                single column
                    ConfigValidationStatus.Status
                        no label
                        display as tag
                            color of red when (ValidationFailed)
                            color of green when (ValidationFailed)
                    ConfigValidationStatus.ValidationErrorText
                        no label
                    ErrorText
